924
01:01:51,860 --> 01:01:54,260
[SCREAMS]

925
01:01:54,620 --> 01:01:55,860
[YELLS]

926
01:01:59,220 --> 01:02:01,220
[SCREAMING]

927
01:02:03,740 --> 01:02:05,340
[SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY]

928
01:02:12,900 --> 01:02:13,900
[SHRIEKING]

929
01:02:15,780 --> 01:02:17,580
[GRUNTS]

930
01:02:21,340 --> 01:02:23,060
Dave?

931
01:02:24,220 --> 01:02:25,580
Dave.

932
01:02:45,020 --> 01:02:46,740
[GASPS]

933
01:02:59,940 --> 01:03:02,500
[EBRILL MUTTERING IN WELSH]

934
01:03:02,540 --> 01:03:05,220
ADELLE:
Where are you?

935
01:03:05,220 --> 01:03:06,420
Ebrill.

936
01:03:07,620 --> 01:03:09,180
[WHIMPERING]

937
01:03:11,060 --> 01:03:13,060
Oh, God.

938
01:03:13,060 --> 01:03:14,900
Oh, my God.

939
01:03:18,900 --> 01:03:22,220
I never meant to hurt anyone.

940
01:03:32,740 --> 01:03:33,900
Adelle?

941
01:03:36,620 --> 01:03:38,140
Adelle?

942
01:03:43,540 --> 01:03:45,620
Oh, Jesus.

943
01:03:45,620 --> 01:03:47,460
[EBRILL SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY IN WELSH]

944
01:04:05,620 --> 01:04:07,540
They died because of me.
No.

945
01:04:07,540 --> 01:04:08,780
Everyone dies
because of me.

946
01:04:08,780 --> 01:04:10,820
No. No one's
gonna die anymore.

947
01:04:10,820 --> 01:04:12,420
You can fix it.

948
01:04:12,460 --> 01:04:13,940
You don't have to do it alone.

949
01:04:13,940 --> 01:04:15,460
