[ANIMAL SNORTS]
[GASPS]

1011
01:08:44,980 --> 01:08:47,540
[SNORTING]

1012
01:09:20,620 --> 01:09:22,140
[WHIMPERING]
[GASPS]

1013
01:09:23,940 --> 01:09:25,820
[CRUNCHING AND SCRAPING]

1014
01:09:30,820 --> 01:09:32,100
[WHIMPERING]

1015
01:09:58,660 --> 01:10:00,820
Where is my daughter?

1016
01:10:02,820 --> 01:10:04,020
Where is she?

1017
01:10:04,020 --> 01:10:08,100
Some little lamb has found
her way out through my wall.

1018
01:10:11,780 --> 01:10:12,740
CHILD'S VOICE:
Mom.

1019
01:10:12,740 --> 01:10:13,860
Sarah?

1020
01:10:13,860 --> 01:10:15,020
Go.
Mom!

1021
01:10:15,020 --> 01:10:17,940
