1065
01:12:29,580 --> 01:12:31,300
Oh, my God, Sarah.
Sarah, come here, baby.

1066
01:12:31,300 --> 01:12:33,220
Come here. Come here.

1067
01:12:33,220 --> 01:12:34,900
That's a girl. Come here, baby.

1068
01:12:36,300 --> 01:12:37,580
Sarah. That's it.

1069
01:12:40,660 --> 01:12:41,620
Sarah.

1070
01:12:41,620 --> 01:12:42,980
