1075
01:12:53,300 --> 01:12:54,780
Yes.

1076
01:12:55,660 --> 01:12:57,540
Don't you want me back, Mom?

1077
01:12:57,540 --> 01:12:58,740
Yes, I do.

1078
01:12:58,740 --> 01:13:01,140
